data.description:
**Multiple offers received. Offer deadline Sat, Nov 27th at 7:00pm. 
Beautiful, mid-century modern home on a large, treed lot in an iconic 60's subdivision. This large, open floorplan features a brick fireplace with multiple built-ins, a drop zone, & a separate utility room with space for a fridge. The kitchen & bathrooms have been remodeled boasting quartz and SS appliances in the kitchen, dual vanities, & a spacious, spa-like shower in the master bath. New paint, lighting, & flooring throughout. The backyard is expansive with a concrete porch perfect for entertaining. Located near UTA and the Arl entertainment district. 
Foundation repaired 2021 with a transferable warranty. The roof is 3 years old.
